---
layout: base.njk
title: Request Received
---

<style>
    .success-container {
        background-color: var(--surface-color);
        padding: var(--spacing-xl);
        border-radius: 12px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: var(--spacing-xl) auto;
        border: 1px solid rgba(230, 92, 0, 0.2);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .success-container h2 {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .success-container p {
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .success-container .home-link {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--fire-main), var(--fire-dark));
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .success-container .home-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(230, 92, 0, 0.4);
    }
</style>

<div class="success-container">
    <h2>Request Sent to Ned</h2>
    <p>You have successfully disturbed Ned for your membership here, watch out for his email for inivitaiton to the
        CMS.</p>
    <a href="/" class="home-link">Return to the Campfire</a>
</div>
